the limit <me>\lim_{ x\to 8 } \frac{ x^{2} - 3 \, x - 40 }{ x^{2} + 4 \, x - 96 }</me>
        </p>
    </statement>
    <answer>
        <p>
            <me>
\begin{array}{c|ccccccc}
x &amp; 7.9&amp; 7.99&amp; 7.999&amp; 8&amp; 8.001&amp; 8.01&amp; 8.1 \\\hline
